snippet.title: Twisted Metal® Revenge Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the Twisted Metal® game at PlayStation's official site: http://goo.gl/2BXJi

With over 1000 kills to his credit, Sweet Tooth is a slasher who's more myth and legend. Watch the new E3 trailer, "Revenge," for a look at Sweet Tooth's unique powers of destruction.

May contain content inappropriate for children. Visit www.esrb.org for rating information.
